description:
Mamma Mia! - Here We Go Again: The Movie Soundtrack Featuring the Songs of ABBA by ABBA

Requirements: .ePUB reader, 22 MB

Overview: (Piano/Vocal/Guitar Songbook). This 2018 sequel/prequel to the popular 2008 film of the same name again features the music of '70s pop sensation ABBA. Our matching songbook includes the songs: Andante, Andante * Angel Eyes * Dancing Queen * Day Before You Came * Fernando * I Have a Dream * I Wonder (Departure) * I've Been Waiting for You * Kisses of Fire * Knowing Me, Knowing You * Mamma Mia * My Love My Life * The Name of the Game * One of Us * Super Trouper * Waterloo * When I Kissed the Teacher * Why Did It Have to Be Me?

Genre: Non-Fiction > General
